modName: Quilue - Dark Elf Woman - Save game
summary:
Some people asked me to upload an early save game of this character.
So here it is. However you must also use the normal map I provided.
descriptionHtml:
[img]http://www.freeimagehosting.net/newuploads/ccc7d.jpg[/img]

- DESCRIPTION -

My attempt at creating a cute dark elf woman.

You start just before going to the block. 
(Sorry too lazy to do Helgen keep again)

- INSTALLATION -

- Put the save game file here :
C:\\Users\\-USERNAME-\\Documents\\My Games\\Skyrim\\Saves

- And extract the data folder in the game directory.
If you have any texture mod,
Click yes when Windows asks if you want to overwrite the file \"femalehead_msn.dds\".

Then you\'re ready to go !


Finally if you want to edit the character appearance,
In game, press ~ to bring up console and type in player.showracemenu
author: DoctorPepper
